msgid "Procedure: Creating an Activation Key"
msgstr "Postup: Vytvoření aktivačního klíče"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:14
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, as an administrator, navigate to menu:"
"Systems[Activation Keys]."
msgstr ""
"V {productname} {webui} jako správce (administrátor) přejděte do menu:"
"Systems[Activation Keys] (Aktivační klíče)."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:15
msgid "Click the btn:[Create Key] button."
msgstr "Klikněte na tlačítko btn:[Create Key] (Vytvořit klíč)."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:16
msgid ""
"On the [guimenu]``Activation Key Details`` page, in the "
"[guimenu]``Description`` field, enter a name for the activation key."
msgstr ""
"Na stránce [guimenu]``Activation Key Details`` (podrobnosti aktivačního "
"klíče) zadejte do pole [guimenu]``Description`` (popis) název aktivačního "
"klíče."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:17
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Key`` field, enter the distribution and service pack "
"associated with the key."
msgstr ""
"Do pole [guimenu]``Key`` (klíč) zadejte distribuci a aktualizaci Service "
"Pack sdruženou s klíčem."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:18
msgid "For example, ``SLES12-SP4`` for {sles}{nbsp}12{nbsp}SP4."
msgstr "Například ``SLES12-SP4`` pro {sles}{nbsp}12{nbsp}SP4."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:19
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:78
msgid ""
"Do not use commas in the [guimenu]``Key`` field for any {suse} products.  "
"However, you *must* use commas for Red Hat Products.  For more information, "
"see xref:reference:systems/activation-keys.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Nepoužívejte čárky v poli [guimenu]``Key`` (klíč) pro produkty {suse}. U "
"produktů Red Hat však *musíte* použít čárky. Další informace viz xref:"
"reference:systems/activation-keys.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:20
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Base Channels`` drop-down box, select the appropriate base "
"software channel, and allow the relevant child channels to populate."
msgstr ""
"V rozbalovacím seznamu [guimenu]``Base Channels`` (základní kanály) vyberte "
"příslušný základní kanál softwaru a povolte používání souvisejících "
"podřízených kanálů."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:21
msgid ""
"For more information, see xref:reference:admin/setup-wizard.adoc#vle.webui."
"admin.wizard.products[] and xref:administration:custom-channels.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Další informace viz xref:reference:admin/setup-wizard.adoc#vle.webui.admin."
"wizard.products[] a xref:administration:custom-channels.adoc[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:22
msgid ""
"Select the child channels you need (for example, the mandatory {susemgr} "
"tools and updates channels)."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte podřízené kanály, které potřebujete (například povinné nástroje "
"{susemgr} a aktualizační kanály)."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:23
msgid ""
"We recommend you leave the [guimenu]``Contact Method`` set to "
"[guimenu]``Default``."
msgstr ""
"Doporučujeme ponechat [guimenu]``Contact Method`` (způsob kontaktu) "
"nastavený na [guimenu]``Default`` (výchozí)."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:24
msgid ""
"We recommend you leave the [guimenu]``Universal Default`` setting unchecked."
msgstr ""
"Doporučujeme ponechat nastavení [guimenu]``Universal Default`` (univerzální "
"výchozí) nezaškrtnuté."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:25
msgid "Click btn:[Create Activation Key] to create the activation key."
msgstr ""
"Stisknutím btn:[Create Activation Key] (vytvořit aktivační klíč) vytvořte "
"aktivační klíč."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:26
msgid ""
"Check the [guimenu]``Configuration File Deployment`` check box to enable "
"configuration management for this key, and click btn:[Update Activation Key] "
"to save this change."
msgstr ""
"Zaškrtnutím možnosti [guimenu]``Configuration File Deployment`` (nasazení "
"konfiguračního souboru) povolíte správu konfigurace pro tento klíč a "
"stisknutím btn:[Update Activation Key] (aktualizovat aktivační klíč) tuto "
"změnu uložíte."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:27
msgid ""
"The [guimenu]``Configuration File Deployment`` check box does not appear "
"until after you have created the activation key.  Ensure you go back and "
"check the box if you need to enable configuration management."
msgstr ""
"Zaškrtávací možnost [guimenu]``Configuration File Deployment`` (nasazení "
"konfiguračního souboru) se zobrazí až po vytvoření aktivačního klíče. "
"Potřebujete-li povolit správu konfigurace, nezapomeňte se vrátit a "
"zaškrtnout tuto možnost."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "Combining Mutiple Activation Keys"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:29
msgid ""
"You can combine activation keys when executing the bootstrap script on your "
"traditional clients.  Combining keys allows for more control on what is "
"installed on your systems and reduces duplication of keys for large or "
"complex environments."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/activation-keys.adoc:30
msgid ""
"Combining activation keys works only on traditional clients.  Salt clients "
"do not support combined activation keys.  If you use a combined key with a "
"Salt client, only the first key is used."
msgstr ""

