#: modules/client-configuration/pages/autoinst-intro.adoc:3
msgid ""
"For most clients, you can use an autoinstallation file.  The "
"autoinstallation file contains information about the distribution to install "
"on the clients.  There are two main types of autoinstallation file:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/autoinst-intro.adoc:4
