"When you have created an autoinstallation file, you can upload and manage it "
"in the {productname} {webui}.  The {webui} also provides tools to help you "
"edit and maintain your autoinstallation files.  For more information about "
"autoinstallation files, see xref:client-configuration:autoinst-setup.adoc[]."
