#, no-wrap
msgid "Provision Bare Metal Systems"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/cobbler.adoc:136
msgid ""
"Provisioning bare metal systems is similar to provisioning other systems, "
"and can be done using the [guilabel]``Provisioning`` tab.  However, you "
"cannot schedule provisioning, it happens automatically as soon as the system "
"is configured and powered on."
